    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trininitatis. <persName
                        key="#Emperor/king #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/124"
                            >Fridericus</persName> dei favente clementia Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> augustus. Si ecclesiarum atque
                        ecclesiasticarum personarum provectibus clementer annuimus et eis profutura
                        gratiose largimur, hoc nobis tam ad temporalis vite prosperitatem quam ad
                        eternam beatitudinem profuturum non ambigimus. Quocirca omnium futurorum et
                        presentium Christi regnique fidelium noverit industria, qualiter nos
                        peticione dilecti principis nostri <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/527">Willehelmi</persName> venerabilis <placeName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/245"><orgName key="#Mother_churches"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/406">Nouariensis</orgName></placeName>
                        civitatis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> universas possessiones, quas
                        ecclesia sua tradicione regum seu imperatorum, largicione pontificum,
                        oblatione fidelium seu aliis quibuscumque iustis modis inpresentiarum
                        possidet vel in futurum possessura est, sub regie auctoritatis <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">tuicionem</rs> et mundiburdium
                        suscepimus et omnia privilegia ecclesie sue ab antecessoribus nostris
                        regibus et imperatoribus collata, spetialiter ab <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130">Henrico</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/173">Ottone</persName> imperatoribus
                        confirmata nos quoque pari donationis voto <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >confirmamus</rs> et lege in perpetutum valitura corroboramus. De
                        possessionibus vero eiusdem ecclesie sue quedam propriis duximus exprimenda
                        vocabulis: ius civitatis, videlicet <rs key="#Districtio">districtum</rs>
                        liberorum hominum et <rs key="#Teloneum">thelonium</rs> et forum, quod
                        quinta feria agitur, et theloneum ac <rs key="#Periodic_markets"
                            >mercatum</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Castle #Ports #Periodic_markets #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#places/525">Gaudiano</placeName> et <rs key="#Shores">ripatum</rs>
                        atque <rs key="#Riverbed">alveum</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4389" key="#Rivers #Riverbed #Shores"
                            >Thicini</placeName> ab eo loco, qui dicitur Camerago, usque ad locum,
                        qui dicitur Petra Maura, <rs key="#Ports">portum</rs> etiam, qui vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Ports" ref="#places/107">Bestanium</placeName>, et <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/848">Materelle</placeName> cum omnibus
                        attinentiis suis, <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus #Teloneum" ref="#estates/327"><placeName
                                key="#Comitatus #Teloneum" ref="#places/733"
                            >Plumbie</placeName></geogName> cum theloneo. Pretera statuimus et regia
                        auctoritate prohibemus, ne aliquis in distrito episcopi castrum edificare
                        vel aliquas municiones sine licentia episcopi facere presumat nec <rs
                            key="#Fodrum">fodrum</rs> vel aliquas exactiones facere vel exigere
                        salvo tamen per omnia iure regio. Insuper adiciendo statuimus, ut nullus
                        successorum nostrorum regum et imperatorum seu alia magna vel parva persona
                        aut potestas prefatam ecclesiam in prenominatis possessionibus seu in
                        ripatico Thicini a predicto loco Bestanni usque in proclivum episcopatus
                        Nouariensis ecclesie seu in aliis quibuscumque possessionibus suis
                        inquietare, molestare, divestire presumat. Quodsi quis presumpserit, regio
                            banno subiaceat et in
                        compositione <rs key="#Penalty">centum libras auri purissimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere
                        nostre</rs> et alteram partem predicte Nouariensi ecclesie et episcopo. Et ut
                        omnia memorate ecclesie et episcopi usibus profutura rata et inconvulsa omni
                        tempore in posterum permaneant, presentem paginam sigilli inpressione
                        communimus adhibitis <rs key="#Witness">testibus</rs>, quorum nomina hec sunt: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Patriarchs" ref="#people/1616">Peregrinus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Patriarchs" ref="#places/2710">Aquileyensis</placeName> <rs key="#Patriarchs"
                            >patriarcha</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Archbishops" ref="#people/1617">Hillinus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Archbishops" ref="#places/1925">Treuerensis</placeName> <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopus</rs>,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Bishops" ref="#people/1620">
                            Euerhardus</persName> <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/1927">Bauenbergensis</placeName> episcopus,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Bishops" ref="#people/1624">Conradus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/1609">Wormaciensis</placeName> episcopus,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Bishops" ref="#people/4077">Hermannus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/4424">Constanciensis</placeName>
                        episcopus, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Bishops" ref="#people/4078">Ortlibus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/1931">Basiliensis</placeName> episcopus,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Abbots" ref="#people/4079">Wibaldus</persName> <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2497">Corbeiensis</orgName> atque
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2498">Stabulensis</orgName> <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Abbots" ref="#people/3787">Marquardus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2478">Wldensis</orgName> abbas, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/1621">Henricus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> Saxonie, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/4080">Henricus</persName> dux Karinthie,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/1623">Bertoldus</persName> dux Burgundie,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Palatine_count" ref="#people/4052">Otto</persName> <rs key="#Palatine_count">palatinus</rs> Bauarie,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/1621">Henricus</persName>
                        marchio Saxonie, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/5033">Odacker</persName> marchio
                        Stirie, <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/4081">Hermannus</persName> marchio de <placeName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#places/59">Verona</placeName>,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/4082">Wilhelmvs</persName> marchi de <placeName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#places/709"></placeName>Monteferrato,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma #Count" ref="#people/4083">Wido</persName> <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> de <placeName key="#Count" ref="#places/4457">Blandrato</placeName> et alii
                        quam plures. Signum domini Friderici Romanorum (M.) regis invictissimi. </ab>
                </div>
